Add MarrySyncTab.jsx — a single workspace backed by the marryModule() engine:
load a married SOURCE + unmarried TARGET, derive→write→verify in one place,
with the confidence badge and the unverified-target ack gate surfaced in-UI.

Consolidation: the 'secsync' entry (front-page 'Security Sync' rail button,
appearance unchanged) now renders MarrySyncTab instead of the read-only
SecuritySyncTab; BcmPcmPairingTab is retired and its id redirects to the
unified tab via TAB_REDIRECTS. Both old component files are kept (reversible).
Drawer drops from 51→50 tabs. esbuild-validated; registry verifier green.
